{"word":"G4787 - συγκινέω - synkinéō - soong-kin-eh'-o - Stir up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συγκινέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synkinéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soong-kin-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Stir up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எழுப்பிவிடு"},{"paragraph":"to move together with others"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4682 - σπαράσσω - sparássō - spar-as'-so/4682\">G4682</a> and <a href=\"#/G2795 - κινέω - kinéō - kin-eh'-o/2795\">G2795</a>; to <i>move together</i>, that is, (specifically) to <i>excite</i> as a mass (to sedition): - stir up.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}